g to the fact what mob he is taunting. Nothing fancy at lower levels but in higher raids with multiple mobs and lots of melee and such, a simple message like &quot;%T is next in line&quot; works great. This also works well for other tanks/nukers to ensure that they have the next mob targeted.<br>
